Script to fetch content from an are.na channel and display it as a modal gallery. Push new content to are.na from a mobile device, instantly refreshes where script is used. Built as a simple RSS style image feed for https://ethan-rubens.com/ 

Setup:
             1. Set ARENA_CHANNEL to your channel slug (line ~120)
             2. Add <a href="#" id="now-trigger">Now</a> anywhere in your page
             3. Drop this <style> block and the HTML + <script> below
                into your project

           Swipe left/right  →  navigate images
           Tap/click outside frame →  close
           Arrow keys        →  navigate (desktop)
           Escape            →  close (desktop) -->
